message:
If you are in the #Orlando area please check out this incredible show. Hidden Tears Project will do 6 performances during Orlando Fringe this week. Their show "RED is a dance theater show about surviving the darkest human experiences and the joy that comes from living through them." Florida Abolitionist will join them to provide information about Human Trafficking in Florida. These are two great organizations that are in the fight against human trafficking. 
#CreatingChange #HelpERASE
